Title: Unnatural Habits
Writer: John Banas (additional story editor), Ysabelle Dean, Kristen Dunphy (additional story editor), Kerry Greenwood (novel)
Actors: Essie Davis, Nathan Page, Hugo Johnstone-Burt, Ashleigh Cummings
Plot: When the death of a teenager leads Jack & Phryne to investigate a halfway house for pregnant and wayward girls they find their investigation blocked at every turn. With Jack's job in jeopardy solving this case just got personal.
